Package lockers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Locker
    Locker is an object that contains the dimensions of what it can fit and any mail that may be in it.
    Mail
    Mail is an object that contains the dimensions of what it can fit inside as well as the recipient it is for.
    Recipient
    Recipient is my super object of a person that contains their first name, last name, and email address.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IncorrectRecipientException
    IncorrectRecipient is an exception created to make sure the correct person is taking the mail out of the locker.
    InvalidSizeException
    InvalidSize is an exception created to make sure the size of the mail and the locker is greater than 0.
    LockerException
    LockerException is created to make sure the locker is empty or will fit the piece of mail trying to be added.
